Special Delivery (V)<br />
Oppressive Enforcement & There Is No Try<br />
<br />
<b>Locations(2) </b><br />
Tatooine (Ep1)<br />
Cloud City: East Platform (Docking Bay)<br />
<br />
<b>Characters(12) </b><br />
IG-88 (V) x2<br />
Boba Fett CC (V) x2<br />
Darth Maul x2<br />
Darth Vader With Lightsaber<br />
Mara Jade, The Emperor’s Hand (V) x2<br />
